videos.description: Giannis Antetokounmpo is fouled by Bruce Brown, who shoves him out of bounds to earn a technical foul.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Bruce Brown gets tech for late shove on Giannis) 2021/06/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Bruce Brown gets tech for late shove on Giannis

videos.description: Kevin Durant goes at Jrue Holiday in the post and somehow gets the floater to fall at an awkward angle.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (How did Durant make this?) 2021/06/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: How did Durant make this?

videos.description: Kevin Durant finds a cutting Bruce Brown who flushes the dunk over Giannis Antetokounmpo.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Brown crams one on Giannis) 2021/06/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Brown crams one on Giannis

videos.description: Giannis Antetokounmpo air-balls the free throw after the crowd counts to 10.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Crowd counts to 10 on Giannis' free throw and he air-balls) 2021/06/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Crowd counts to 10 on Giannis' free throw and he air-balls

videos.description: Giannis Antetokounmpo banks in the 3 and lets the crowd know he called it.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Giannis claims he called glass on banked 3) 2021/06/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Giannis claims he called glass on banked 3

videos.description: P.J. Tucker called for a hard foul on Kevin Durant and while KD is shooting free throws, he has some fun with Durant's mom sitting courtside.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (KD's mom has fun with PJ Tucker after hard foul on Durant) 2021/06/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: KD's mom has fun with PJ Tucker after hard foul on Durant

videos.description: Jrue Holiday drives and finds a cutting Giannis Antetokounmpo who flushes it home plus the foul.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Giannis crams dunk in traffic) 2021/06/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Giannis crams dunk in traffic

videos.description: A broken play leads to a Kevin Durant dunk and he is pumped.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Durant fired up after and-1 dunk) 2021/06/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Durant fired up after and-1 dunk

videos.description: James Harden somehow gets the three to fall after hitting it off glass.
videos.headline: Harden banks in tough 3

videos.description: Kevin Durant hits the incredible two-pointer with his foot on the line to tie the game at 109-109.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (KD's off-balanced two sends game to OT) 2021/06/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: KD's off-balanced two sends game to OT

videos.description: Kevin Durant goes for the winner and can't convert the 3-pointer as the Bucks advance to the Eastern Conference finals.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (KD can't convert late in OT, Bucks advance to ECF) 2021/06/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: KD can't convert late in OT, Bucks advance to ECF

videos.description: Khris Middleton drains a turnaround jumper to put the Bucks ahead of the Nets for good.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Middleton's clutch jumper in OT caps Bucks' Game 7 win) 2021/6/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Middleton's clutch jumper in OT caps Bucks' Game 7 win

videos.description: Tim Legler commends the Bucks for persevering in their overtime win vs. the Nets in Game 7.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Analysis (Legler: Bucks 'shared the burden' in OT win vs. Nets) 2021/6/19 ESHEET SC

videos.headline: Legler: Bucks 'shared the burden' in OT win vs. Nets

videos.description: The Bucks and Nets go down to the wire in a wild fourth quarter and overtime as Milwaukee comes out on top and advances to the Eastern Conference finals.
